                    a deep understanding of business requirements to deliver
                    solutions that truly make a difference.
                </p>

                {
                    !brief && (
                        <a
                            href="/about"
                            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary-600 hover:text-primary-700 font-medium mt-6 transition-colors"
                        >
                            Learn more about me
                            <svg
                                class="w-4 h-4"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor"
                                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            >
                                <path
                                    stroke-linecap="round"
                                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"
